div.p:
If the same day there be a Celebration of the Holy Communion in the Church;
                  Reservation of the Sacrament.
                   then shall the Priest reserve (at the Open Communion) so much of the Sacrament of CHRIST's Body and Blood, as shall serve the Sick Person; and as Many as shall Communicate with him (if there be any) (fol. cxliv.)
